Package: avanzaR
Type: Package
Title: Unofficial Client for the Avanza API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Saw", "Simeon", email = "saw.s@ku.th", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Saw Simeon <saw.s@ku.th>
Description: An unofficial R client for the Avanza API. Fetch account data, place orders, and retrieve performance reports from Sweden's Avanza brokerage. The API is unofficial and may change without notice. Use at your own risk.
